OL,3,CFree school meals to be extended to
OL,4,Cmore secondary school pupils
OL,6,FMore secondary school aged pupils in
OL,7,FWales will be able to get free school
OL,8,Fmeals, the Welsh Government has
OL,9,Fannounced.
OL,11,FCurrently pupils are only eligible for
OL,12,Ffree school meals if their family
OL,13,Freceives Universal Credit and their
OL,14,Fhousehold earnings are less than
OL,15,F#7,400.
OL,17,FAll primary school pupils get free
OL,18,Fschool meals.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
