OL,3,CFree school meals to be extended to
OL,4,Cmore secondary school pupils
OL,6,FThe Plaid Cymru Welsh Government has
OL,7,Fannounced #15m to expand the free
OL,8,Fschool meals provision for secondary
OL,9,Fschool age pupils in households by
OL,10,Fremoving the income limit.
OL,12,FThe policy is expected to be rolled
OL,13,Fout from September.
OL,15,FThe government says the funding will
OL,16,Fbe split into #10m of capital funding,
OL,17,Fto invest in school kitchen and dining
OL,18,Fareas, and #5m of revenue funding for
OL,19,Fintroducing the scheme.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
