OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1782051073
OL,3,CFree school meals to be extended to
OL,4,Cmore secondary school pupils
OL,6,FThe announcement comes before Plaid
OL,7,FCymru is expected to announce its
OL,8,Fsupplementary budget on Tuesday.
OL,10,FCabinet Minister for Education and
OL,11,FWelsh Language, Anna Brychan, said:
OL,12,F"This funding marks the first step in
OL,13,Four commitment to extend free school
OL,14,Fmeals to more secondary pupils,
OL,15,Fensuring that support reaches families
OL,16,Fwho need it most.
OL,18,F"By starting to invest, we are laying
OL,19,Fthe foundations for a fair and
OL,20,Fsustainable expansion that will make a
OL,21,Freal difference in pupils' daily lives.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
