PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1782051073
OL,3,CFree school meals to be extended to
OL,4,Cmore secondary school pupils
OL,6,F"This work is about removing barriers
OL,7,Fto learning and supporting wellbeing.
OL,8,FWe know that access to nutritious food
OL,9,Fimproves concentration, attainment and
OL,10,Foverall health.
OL,12,F"Building on the success of universal
OL,13,Fprimary free school meals, we will
OL,14,Fensure that as children move into
OL,15,Fsecondary education those who need it
OL,16,Fmost will continue to receive the
OL,17,Fsupport they need to thrive.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
