OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1782051073
OL,3,CFree school meals to be extended to
OL,4,Cmore secondary school pupils
OL,6,F"We are working with partners on plans
OL,7,Fto deliver this effectively and at
OL,8,Fpace ensuring every pound delivers the
OL,9,Fgreatest possible benefit for the
OL,10,Fpeople of Wales. Further details will
OL,11,Fbe announced shortly."
